            <div type="translation">
                <p>Asklepiades, farewell!</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The text implies the vocative + salutation formula which is found several times at Mineo, and
                    reproduced in the latin epitaph engraved on the reverse of this stone (<ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic3447">ISic3447</ref>)
                </p>
